                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The torn trio has a creature grappled or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Restrained] by at least two limbs</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The creature takes @Damage[(5d6+2)[slashing]] damage for each limb currently grabbing or restraining it (maximum 15d6), with a @Check[fortitude|dc:30|basic] save. On a critical failure, the creature also loses a random body part, and one of the torn trio's limbs is now no longer grabbing or restraining it.</p>"
                },
